2. **High Priority:** Fix on-chain hospital milestone confirmation  
3. **Medium Priority:** Add smart contract refund function
4. **Medium Priority:** Complete MetaMask wallet integration end-to-end
5. **Low Priority:** Cross-document name verification, hospital trust weighting
6. **Low Priority:** Encryption at rest, HIPAA/GDPR compliance
